  <h3>Our Values</h3>
	<ol>
	  <li><strong>Ethics and Integrity</strong>: UdM upholds honesty, fairness, and transparency in all its activities, ensuring trust and accountability among students, staff, and stakeholders.</li>
	  <li><strong>Service and Support</strong>: The university prioritizes the well-being of its community, offering resources and assistance to help individuals thrive academically and personally.</li>
	  <li><strong>Reliability and Excellence</strong>: UdM consistently delivers high-quality education and services, maintaining a dependable reputation in Mauritius and internationally.</li>
	  <li><strong>Adaptability and Responsiveness</strong>: The university listens to the needs of its community and adjusts its programs and approaches to stay relevant in a rapidly evolving world.</li>
	  <li><strong>Inclusivity and Diversity</strong>: UdM celebrates and welcomes people from all backgrounds, fostering an environment of mutual respect and understanding.</li>
	  <li><strong>Sustainability and Environmental Awareness</strong>: The institution actively promotes practices that protect the planet and contribute to sustainable development.</li>
	  <li><strong>Innovation and Creativity</strong>: UdM encourages bold thinking and the exploration of new ideas, allowing its community to push the boundaries of what is possible.</li>
	  <li><strong>Continuous Learning and Growth</strong>: The university embraces change and improvement, constantly seeking to refine its programs, research, and impact.</li>
	</ol>
</div>